				<div class="talk-intro">
					<p id="tagline" class="notranslate">In his lab at Penn, Vijay Kumar and his team build flying quadrotors, small, agile robots that swarm, sense each other, and form ad hoc teams -- for construction, surveying disasters and far more.</p>
											<p>
							At the University of Pennsylvania, Vijay Kumar studies the control and coordination of multi-robot formations. <a target="_blank" title="Vijay Kumar's bio" href="/speakers/vijay_kumar.html">Full bio »</a>						</p>
					
